OL,3,CSchoolgirls carry out 'cruel' attack
OL,4,Cthat leaves hedgehog dead, charity says
OL,6,FA hedgehog which was "thrown up in the
OL,7,Fair and buried alive" has died after
OL,8,Fbeing attacked by three school girls,
OL,9,Fa charity has said.
OL,11,FThree girls aged between 10-12 are
OL,12,Freported to have thrown the hedgehog -
OL,13,Fnicknamed 'Hedgy' by volunteers - down
OL,14,Fa slide, before burying him alive in a
OL,15,Fplant pot, at Greenhill Community Hub
OL,16,Fin Skelmersdale.
OL,18,FTwo boys who saw what happened and
OL,19,Freported the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
