PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779304271
OL,3,CSchoolgirls carry out 'cruel' attack
OL,4,Cthat leaves hedgehog dead, charity says
OL,6,FHedgy was taken to Haydock Hedgehog
OL,7,FHelpers Rescue in St Helens,
OL,8,FMerseyside, where he was treated with
OL,9,Fpainkillers and put in an incubator.
OL,11,FIn an update shared on Tuesday 19 May,
OL,12,Fthe charity confirmed the hedgehog had
OL,13,Fdied.
OL,15,FRescuer Kelly Leyland said she was
OL,16,F"disgusted and angry" at the attack.
OL,17,FShe said: "Instead of finding kind
OL,18,Fpeople to help him, he was thrown
OL,19,Faround like a toy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779304271
OL,3,CSchoolgirls carry out 'cruel' attack
OL,4,Cthat leaves hedgehog dead, charity says
OL,6,FShe said that because of his
OL,7,Fcondition, Hedgy would probably not
OL,8,Fhave been able to curl into a ball to
OL,9,Fdefend himself, meaning he could not
OL,10,Fuse his spines as natural protection
OL,11,Ffrom the blows.
OL,13,FKelly said: "It's taken so much of my
OL,14,Fenergy, it's really draining. It's
OL,15,Falso taking away from me caring for
OL,16,Fthe other hedgehogs as much as they
OL,17,Fneed."
OL,19,FIt's understood Lancashire police are
OL,20,Finvestigating the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
